    <h1>Resource Directory for the Z39.86-2010 Simple Book Profile, version 0.1</h1> 
    <p>The Z39.86-2010 Simple Book Profile is intended to serve as an XML republishing format for print books with a simple structure, such as novels, children's books, non-complicated text books, some types of manuals, etc.</p>
    <p>This profile is not designed to meet the requirements for markup of more complicated text books, reference books, science etc.</p>
    
    <p>Maintenance agency information goes here.</p>
    <p>This document is compliant with 
	<a href="http://www.rddl.org">Resource Directory Description Language (RDDL)</a> 1.0, version February 18, 2002.</p>
    <p>The canonical URI for this Resource Directory is <code>http://www.daisy.org/z3986/2010/simplebook/1.0/</code>.</p>

